<p>
The Burnside site is approximately 3.32 hectares. The site can be accessed from either Ancaster Way or Burnside / Snakey Path.  There are 99 full plots, about 50 of which are divided and let as half plots.  
There are 7 water troughs on the site: these are supplied with water from spring to autumn. Most plots are no further than 25 metres from the nearest water trough. 
The site also has a composting toilet and a picnic area.
</p>
